name: Charli D'Amelio
description:
Charli D'Amelio of TikTok etc. 
Who should I do next?

Lower CFG gives best results, I hang out around 4.5.

test prompt in a few images. I use a system the uses <> for TI triggers, remove those if your UI doesn't utilize that.

Using my own model blend in the examples, it's basically a mix of Deliberate, Liberty, URPM, Onemix, and I'm really not sure what else, but the embedding works well in most models I've tried.

Trained at 4012 steps on 59 images.

This is my second upload, any reviews are appreciated! And I'd love to see your results!
